</p><p><b>Months (2 bytes): </b> Bit flags that specify on
which months of the year the trigger fires, which are interpreted as specified
in section <a href="5ba70e9b-c0f1-49f6-9aae-b52231346108" data-linktype="relative-path">2.4.2.11.4</a>. </p><p><b>Padding (2 bytes): </b>MUST be set to zero when
sent and MUST be ignored on receipt.</p><p><b>Reserved2 (2 bytes): </b>MUST be set to zero when
sent and MUST be ignored on receipt.</p><p><b>Reserved3 (2 bytes): </b>MUST be set to zero when
sent and MUST be ignored on receipt.</p></div>